result.name: K Square

reviews.text: Great small bar, which are not many, if any, in this area. Pizza was not perfect  but very tasty. Excellent bar to stop for drinks and food.
Small bar with good food just on the streets. Late evenings are good.

Good German beer. Nice clean bar for people watching. Pizza was like a chef boyardee recipe but still edible. I’ll go back for a beer or two. No pizza next time. Maybe a burger or just have beer for dinner.

Having Lunch at around 2pm. Only me as the customer as it is a Bar which is always crowded at night. Highly impressive with the Burger which is excellent of the Beef. It is fresh and juicy. Deep French Fries are just fried. Upgraded drink with Beer (just half price of the menu). Lunch set from 12noon-5pm. Without 10% service charge at lunch. Altogether with soup just $113!  Highly recommended.
Jun 2017
Happy hour
